    o allow specifying credentials in multiple ways
0.0.5
    o S3-based package structure with object for jenkins server/connection and
      an object for job
    o various new functions e.g. to request build history
    o include a vignette on creating packamon jobs through rjenkins
0.0.4
    o create packamon job based local git repo settings
0.0.3
    o ability to create and list jobs
0.0.2
    o introduce function to fetch build logs
0.0.1
